:INFO
🏆 Slate Tournament
Host a community slate tournament with open voting and a jury for a specific \
niche. The winner gets a cash prize, public recognition, and a permanent \
custom label on their slate.

:INFO
💻 Chip: Code
A syntax-highlighted code block chip with line numbers, language detection, \
and copy-to-clipboard. Built for developer slates and technical writing.

:INFO
🧪 Chip: Formula
Render mathematical formulas as a chip using standard notation. Useful for \
science, finance, and education slates.

:INFO
🍔 Chip: Food
Log a meal with type (breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack), price, and a photo. \
Useful for food diaries, restaurant guides, and recipe slates.

:INFO
📺 Chip: YouTube Embed
Embed a YouTube video directly in a slate as a first-class chip. No links, \
no redirects, just the video inline.

:INFO
💭 Chip: Memory
A timestamped, non-editable chip for capturing moments. Add a quote, \
a photo, and a location stamp to preserve something as it was.

:INFO
🎵 Chip: Audio
An inline audio player chip. Useful for podcasts, voice notes, music \
previews, and any slate where sound matters.

:INFO
🎭 Chip: GIF
Search and embed GIFs via Giphy integration. A lightweight way to add \
motion and personality to any slate.

:INFO
📅 Chip: Calendar
Embed a calendar view as a chip. A single day, a weekly agenda, or a \
monthly overview, each linkable to a slate or event.

:INFO
🗓️ Chip: Timeline Event
A horizontal milestone chip with a tick, title, date, and description. \
Great for project histories, personal timelines, and launch sequences.

:INFO
🗳️ Chip: Poll
Let visitors vote on a question. Multiple choice, optional deadline, \
and a results graph that updates in real time.

:INFO
🤖 Chip: Agent
A chip that runs a prompt on a schedule. Daily check-ins, coaching \
nudges, or automated summaries, all inside a slate.

:INFO
🧭 Chip: Itinerary
A route map chip with ordered waypoints connected by road, plane, or \
straight line. Built for travel slates and event planning.

:INFO
🌤️ Chip: Weather
Show live or forecast weather for a location. Useful for travel slates, \
event pages, and any content tied to a place or date.

:INFO
₿ Chip: Crypto Prices
Display live crypto prices via the CoinGecko API. A single token or \
a small watchlist, always current.

:INFO
🎫 Chip: Ticket
A lanyard-style chip for tickets and certificates. Title, date, holder \
name, and a scannable code, all in one card.

:INFO
💕 Chip Likes
Let visitors like individual chips inside a slate, a lightweight signal that \
surfaces what resonates most within a page.

:INFO
⭐ Chip: Rating
Collect star ratings from visitors on any chip. Useful for product reviews, \
recommendations, and feedback-driven slates.

:INFO
⏱️ Chip: Countdown
A live countdown chip that ticks toward a date or event. Launches, \
deadlines, and release dates displayed in real time.

:INFO
🛒 Chip: Product
Sell directly from a slate chip. Add an image, price, and checkout link. \
Native commerce without leaving the slate.

:INFO
💸 Chip: Donation
Accept tips from visitors via a dedicated chip. Simple, low-friction support \
for creators who want to let their audience contribute.

:INFO
🗺️ Chip: Map
Embed a location or event map chip. Useful for travel slates, event pages, \
and any content where place matters.

:CONTACT
What would you add?
